HEADWORD: Soapfish
<hw>Soap"fish`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any serranoid fish of the genus <gen>Rhypticus</gen>; -- so called
from the soapy feeling of its skin.</def>⟦br⟧
